h3 Pills
p.-text Use the <code>pill</code> attribute to render badges with a more pronounced border-radius.
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--2
    chi-badge(class='-m--1', pill)= 'Badge'
  :code(lang="html")
    <chi-badge pill>Badge</chi-badge>

h3 Icon badges
p.-text Icons can be placed before, after, or on both sides of text.
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--2
    chi-badge(class='-m--1')
      chi-icon(icon='plus', size='xs')
      span Badge
    chi-badge(class='-m--1')
      span Badge
      chi-icon(icon='x', size='xs')
    chi-badge(class='-m--1', flat, color='success')
      chi-icon(icon='circle')
      span Active
    chi-badge(class='-m--1', flat, color='warning')
      chi-icon(icon='circle-clock')
      span Away
    chi-badge(class='-m--1', flat, color='danger')
      chi-icon(icon='circle-minus')
      span Do not Disturb
    chi-badge(class='-m--1', flat, color='muted')
      chi-icon(icon='circle')
      span Offline
  :code(lang="html")
    <chi-badge>
      <chi-icon icon='plus'></chi-icon>
      <span>Badge</Badge>
    </chi-badge>
    <chi-badge>
      <span>Badge</Badge>
      <chi-icon icon='x'></chi-icon>
    </chi-badge>
    <chi-badge flat color='success'>
      <chi-icon icon='circle'></chi-icon>
      <span>Active</Badge>
    </chi-badge>
    <chi-badge flat color='warning'>
      <chi-icon icon='circle-clock'></chi-icon>
      <span>Away</Badge>
    </chi-badge>
    <chi-badge flat color='danger'>
      <chi-icon icon='circle-minus'></chi-icon>
      <span>Do not Disturb</Badge>
    </chi-badge>
    <chi-badge flat color='muted'>
      <chi-icon icon='circle'></chi-icon>
      <span>Offline</Badge>
    </chi-badge>

h3 Additional Sizes
h4 Small
p.-text Set the attribute <code>size</code> to <code>small</code> to render small badges.
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--2
    chi-badge(size='small', class='-m--1')= 'Badge'
    chi-badge(size='small', class='-m--1', flat)
      chi-icon(icon='atom')
      span Badge
  :code(lang="html")
    <chi-badge size='small'>Badge</chi-badge>
    <chi-badge size='small' flat>
      <chi-icon icon='atom'></chi-icon>
      <span>Badge</span>
    </chi-badge>
h4 Smaller
p.-text Set the attribute <code>size</code> to <code>smaller</code> to render even smaller badges.
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--2
    chi-badge(size='smaller', class='-m--1')= 'Badge'
    chi-badge(size='smaller', class='-m--1', flat)
      chi-icon(icon='atom')
      span Badge
  :code(lang="html")
    <chi-badge size='smaller'>Badge</chi-badge>
    <chi-badge size='smaller' flat>
      <chi-icon icon='atom'></chi-icon>
      <span>Badge</span>
    </chi-badge>
h3 Text Transform
h4 Uppercase
p.-text Set the <code>text-transform</code> attribute to <code>uppercase</code> to render badges in uppercase,
  | <code>lowercase</code> to render badges in lowercase and <code>capitalized</code> to render badges as capitalized.
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--2
    chi-badge(text-transform='uppercase')= 'Badge'
  :code(lang="html")
    <chi-badge text-transform='uppercase'>Badge</chi-badge>
